In a dark tattoo parlour over one tumultuous afternoon, a group of schoolgirls flirt with boys and danger and are shocked by what they discover.Exploring the mix of supreme self-confidence and vulnerability that comes with being a teenager, At the Tattooist is an atmospheric and sensitive coming-of-age story about growing up, getting in trouble and good friends.
